---
---
  <section id="servizi" class="py-20 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="fade flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-4 mb-12">
        <div>
          <div
            class="inline-block bg-orange-light text-orange text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">
            Cosa faccio</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">I miei servizi</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 font-light max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed">Dalla prima analisi al cambio contratto,
          seguo tutto io. Tu non devi fare altro che dirmi di sì.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-gray-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 fade d1">
        <div class="bg-white p-7 group hover:bg-cream transition-colors relative">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-blue-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">📊</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Analisi bolletta</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">Leggo la tua bolletta, identifico le voci inutili
            e ti spiego esattamente cosa stai pagando e perché.</p>
          <a href="#contatti"
            class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-7 h-7 bg-gray-100 group-hover:bg-blue group-hover:text-white text-gray-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs transition-all group-hover:rotate-45">→</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-7 group hover:bg-cream transition-colors relative">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-orange-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">🔄</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cambio fornitore</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">Confronto le offerte dei principali operatori e
            gestisco tutta la pratica di cambio. Zero burocrazia da parte tua.</p>
          <a href="#contatti"
            class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-7 h-7 bg-gray-100 group-hover:bg-orange group-hover:text-white text-gray-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs transition-all group-hover:rotate-45">→</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-7 group hover:bg-cream transition-colors relative">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-green-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">🏢</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Consulenza aziendale</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">Per negozi, PMI e imprese. Gestisco contratti
            multi-fornitura e trovo le tariffe business più vantaggiose.</p>
          <a href="#contatti"
            class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-7 h-7 bg-gray-100 group-hover:bg-green group-hover:text-white text-gray-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs transition-all group-hover:rotate-45">→</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-7 group hover:bg-cream transition-colors relative">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-blue-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Assistenza post-contratto</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">Rimango disponibile dopo la firma. Bollette
            errate, variazioni, problemi: sono il tuo punto di riferimento.</p>
          <a href="#contatti"
            class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-7 h-7 bg-gray-100 group-hover:bg-blue group-hover:text-white text-gray-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs transition-all group-hover:rotate-45">→</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-7 group hover:bg-cream transition-colors relative">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-orange-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mercato libero</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">Ti spiego la differenza tra mercato tutelato e
            libero e come orientarti nel passaggio obbligatorio.</p>
          <a href="#contatti"
            class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-7 h-7 bg-gray-100 group-hover:bg-orange group-hover:text-white text-gray-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs transition-all group-hover:rotate-45">→</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-7 group hover:bg-cream transition-colors relative">
          <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-green-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5">🌱</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Energia rinnovabile</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">Offerte green da fonti rinnovabili, senza
            rinunciare alla convenienza economica. Scelta sostenibile e intelligente.</p>
          <a href="#contatti"
            class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 w-7 h-7 bg-gray-100 group-hover:bg-green group-hover:text-white text-gray-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs transition-all group-hover:rotate-45">→</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
